---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Knowly">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none">
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 4, 2025</p>

      <h2>Your Privacy Matters</h2>
      <p>
        At Knowly, we believe your personal lessons and reflections are private.
        This policy explains how we handle your data.
      </p>

      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Knowly stores your lessons locally on your device. We do not collect,
        store, or have access to the content of your lessons.
      </p>

      <h3>Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        We may collect anonymous usage analytics to improve the app, such as:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>App opens and feature usage (anonymized)</li>
        <li>Crash reports</li>
        <li>Device type and OS version</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        Your lessons are stored locally on your device. If you use iCloud sync,
        your data is synced through Apple's iCloud service according to Apple's
        privacy policy.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties for
        marketing purposes.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
        privacy@getknowlyapp.com.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
